{"lastModified":1765549161464,"uri":"c::19120700503::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Bahamas\n\nThe 108′ /  32.92m Johnson 108 motor yacht ‘She’s A Peach’ was built in 2016 by Johnson Yachts. Previously named Lone Star her luxurious interior is designed by Johnson Yachts and her exterior styling is by Bill Dixon.\n\nACCOMMODATION\nShe’s A Peach’s interior layout sleeps up to 10 guests in 5 rooms, including a master suite, 1 VIP stateroom, 2 double cabins and 1 twin cabin. She is also capable of carrying up to 4 crew onboard to ensure a relaxed luxury yacht experience. Timeless styling, beautiful furnishings and sumptuous seating feature throughout to create an elegant and comfortable atmosphere.\n\nHer generous deck areas play host to a wide range of amenities including an outdoor bar and ample space for sun lounging and relaxing. She’s A Peach’s impressive leisure and entertainment facilities make her the ideal charter yacht for socializing and entertaining with family and friends.\n\nPERFORMANCE\nShe is built with Fiberglass hull and GRP superstructure. She’s A Peach is capable of 21 knots flat out, with a cruising speed of 18 knots from her 15,142-litre fuel tanks.\n\nAMENITIES\nAir Conditioning, Outdoor Bar, Sun Deck, Sunpads, Swimming Platform, Garage","blueprint":{"name":"SHE'S A PEACH","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f8a17a20-3585-11f0-979a-3dc82af11d28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f8908a30-3585-11f0-979a-3dc82af11d28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f89fcc70-3585-11f0-979a-3dc82af11d28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f8a0dde0-3585-11f0-979a-3dc82af11d28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7892-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb7237